leadership-approach|vision_results_people_process|narrowing_3|3|Before Process is added|People can add range before Process is brought in deliberately, but the pattern may still narrow if Process is left until later. The likely miss is energy that depends on individual effort because the method is not yet clear enough to repeat, especially when Vision and Results already feel convincing.|process|active|leadership-approach::vision_results_people_process::narrowing_3
